---
title: Chicken, White Bean & Couscous Soup with Parsley & Crème Fraîche
description: This soul-warming vegetarian soup is the culinary equivalent of a cozy blanket. It’s chock full of goodness: earthy cannellini beans, tender onion, carrot, and zucchini; plus springy couscous in a savory mushroom-tomato broth. Throw in lots of fresh herbs and a dollop of creme fraiche and it makes an ideal vegetarian dinner or lunch idea! Get ready to wrap yourself in this meal that’s as satisfying and comforting as it is delicious.
